WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:03:00.033 --> 00:03:09.071
Ugh, this is bad! Make soldiers calm down no matter what!
We need our squad to regroup and go meet up with Karin-sama!

00:03:09.171 --> 00:03:11.468
Soldier: Yes!

00:03:16.352 --> 00:03:22.838
Ken-dono! We've opened the path towards Sousou!

00:03:22.938 --> 00:03:27.164
Thank you, Sai! ...Shishun!

00:03:27.364 --> 00:03:29.845
Yes!

00:03:29.945 --> 00:03:35.491
Open the path towards Sousou with the ringing of your bell!

00:03:35.591 --> 00:03:42.265
Your will! Witness this Kan Kouha's strength!

00:03:42.365 --> 00:03:49.359
Raise my banners! Kan Kouha will walk the path of carnage!

00:03:49.459 --> 00:03:53.092
Soldiers: Yes!

00:03:53.192 --> 00:04:01.915
Following Kannei squad, Ryomo squad will also 
advance! Everyone, please follow my banner!

00:04:02.015 --> 00:04:05.718
Soldiers: Yes!

00:04:05.818 --> 00:04:12.908
Send the soldiers of Gi on the road of death! Follow my banners!

00:04:13.008 --> 00:04:16.376
Soldiers: Yes!

